body.name: Napkin Holder for Table St. Patrick's Day Shamrock Clear Paper Towel Napkin Holders Standing Napkin Dispenser for Kitchen, Bathroom, Dining Table, Countertop
features: Size - Measrues 4.1x4.9x1.97in (LxWxH), Which can hold about 50-60 napkins, suitable for kind of types of paper towels and napkins.

Premium Materials - Our farmhouse napkin holder made of clear acrylic, Compared with glass and metal materials, it is more durable, not easy to break, will not oxidise and rust, very suitable for indoor and outdoor use.
Tissue Paper Dispenser - This U-shaped freestanding napkin holder requires no assembly and is easy to load or retrieve, windproof and dustproof, and keeps paper towels and countertops tidy.
Versatile - This upright napkin holder is stable, non-slip and won't damage countertops, perfect for kitchen, dining table, party, buffet, bar, restaurant or bathroom countertops.

Ideal Gifts - This personalised napkin organiser is a unique countertop decoration for a variety of scenarios, suitable as a birthday, wedding, anniversary, housewarming gift for your loved ones and friends around you.
